{"tid":1617363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於今晚康怡廣場既處理手法 我有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-10-03T18:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T01:32:39.000Z","uid":194619,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ec42cdaf0619d0edb87da14ffd66e9928ece03","tid":1617363,"uid":194619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"我dllm出面淨係多人咩事都冇就開始鎖後門唔俾人出入 個保安仲要係咁叫人係正門走 完全製造緊恐慌<br />\n9點幾開始趕人走 話Aeon要關門 <br />\n好啦到放tg啦 防暴推緊上去 啲保安就叫人快啲走出商場<br />\n但一行出去已經有成班防暴係度<br />\n冇幾耐正門落埋閘 得翻側門 有街坊中tg入Aeon避下<br />\n然後啲保安又開始屌鬼 話唔好留係度 又話可以上員工通道走<br />\n但係個員工通道喺戲院個邊 根本冇分別<br />\n<br />\n曾經有問過啲保安點解要咁做 佢地就話都係跟上頭Order做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜真係有必要咁早鎖曬啲門咩 放tg個陣啲街坊根本入唔到去避<br />\n仲要之前811個陣有舖頭想早收就俾Aeon話<br />\n今日就手腳咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAeon安全至上 鎖曬啲門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAeon 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f12cb8dd7d77117e3d2adaf2b1c4acbf3c2373","tid":1617363,"uid":194619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:16:50.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"5536950386ec7f1e259313a96c3635d4965fbbae","tid":1617363,"uid":194619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:17:15.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"4d8d46d2b05b98e902adb31b37a0643e2ecbb896","tid":1617363,"uid":194619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:17:40.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"56ee87d34610f0358cbe52e68926496126922bf1","tid":1617363,"uid":194619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:17:59.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"ebc93dc39b44cba3269626b4cc8f959df9fb0fa3","tid":1617363,"uid":194619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:18:09.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"88145a604c6